title: Crunk Hits Volume 1 [2005] 320kbps
description:
Album Info

Crunk Hits features 18 of the crunkest commercial singles of the preceding few years. Some of these songs were huge hits, like Usher's "Yeah!," Lil Jon's "Get Low," Chingy's "Right Thurr," Ciara's "Goodies," and Juvenile's "Slow Motion." Others, like Killer Mike's "A.D.I.D.A.S." and Jacki-O's "Pussy (Real Good)," weren't really hits, at least not on the same scale, but they were commercial singles and fit in well stylistically with the actual hits here. So the CD flows very well, since all of these songs share the same style -- club-oriented Dirty South
